<h3 id="faq-why-we-are-using-jpa-annotation-instead-of-hibernate">FAQ: Why we are using JPA Annotation instead of Hibernate?</h3>
<hr />
<p>ANSWER:
JPA is a standard specification. Hibernate is an implementation of the JPA specification.</p>

<p>Hibernate implements all of the JPA annotations.</p>

<p>The Hibernate team recommends the use of JPA annotations as a best practice.</p>

